Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 其實我獨自出來露營了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小凜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,現在剛到露營場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪座露營場？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那是秘密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不然給彼此發露營場的照片 來猜猜看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:56.06,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}註︰今天看得真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小凜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天氣這麼晴朗 真是太好啦
